In this Project I am making a windows form where user can input any number greater than 500 as Subtotal and the program will calculate the Discount percentage, Discount amount and Total for them.
I also developed the program where user can use Enter button to calculate their Subtotal without clicking the button and also can use tab button to go to different Textboxes.If the user put any invalid character other than number it will show Zero as output rather than giving an error messege.
